            <title>[PDFBOX-3435] Text extraction - words on same line detection failing in 2.x</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3435</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ability to extract a line of text  as it appears in the PDF is no longer working in the 2.x version of pdfbox.&lt;/p&gt;

