                            <comment id="15408035" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 4 Aug 2016 16:17:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1755201 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1755201&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1755201&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3435&quot; title=&quot;Text extraction - words on same line detection failing in 2.x&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3435&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3435&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: use CapHeight when glyphHeight is 0&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15408037" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 4 Aug 2016 16:17:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1755202 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/2.0&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1755202&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1755202&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3435&quot; title=&quot;Text extraction - words on same line detection failing in 2.x&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3435&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3435&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: use CapHeight when glyphHeight is 0&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15408055" author="tilman" created="Thu, 4 Aug 2016 16:26:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The cause of the problem was that the fonts in your have a (0 0 0 0) bounding box, and the text was not exactly at same height, so PDFBox thought it was on different lines. The modification is to use the CapHeight in this case. I have attached the text extraction (oops, I didn&apos;t use the sort option, but the output seems to be the same) with both versions.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15408074" author="tilman" created="Thu, 4 Aug 2016 16:36:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A snapshot build will be available at &lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfbox-app/2.0.3-SNAPSHOT/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repository.apache.org/content/groups/snapshots/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfbox-app/2.0.3-SNAPSHOT/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
within hours.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve also added your file to my private test set. Thanks for the report!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15410603" author="leevanh" created="Sat, 6 Aug 2016 12:34:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fantastic, this is perfect, it is working great. Thanks for taking the time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
